{
  "stem": "3874.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They split us into two groups.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was in a group that went to the OSE-- one of the OSE homes of Montmorency called Villa-- well, it makes no difference.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it was in Montmorency.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The second group went to a different home, called Chateau Legette, which was run and financed by Baron the Rothschild, with approximately 130 children going over there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were both German children and Austrian children, going over there, going to Chateau Legette, as well as the OSE, there were Austrian and German-- and German kids.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyway, the-- the name of the house was Villa Helvetia in Montmorency, and that's where I was sent.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But again, I had already met some German children, and we started making friends.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was-- I was very, very impressed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember the first days in Montmorency, we walked into the-- we walked into this house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And what the people had done over there, they had set up little tables, for the smaller children, for 10-year-olds.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They were our size.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we could eat, and play, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But it was all colorful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were-- the tables were in blues and reds and yellows.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was really very nicely done, and made us feel very much-- it's a nice place to be.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Well, it turned out it was a very nice place to be.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "However, more and more children kept coming in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so the OSE needed more homes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And consequently, there were two more homes set up in the outskirts of Paris.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "One of them-- one of them in Eaubonne, called Villa Chesnaie, which was for the more orthodox kids.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I was transferred from Montmorency to Eaubonne, to this particular place, where I stayed until I left, until occupation.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
